than it is for a woman in the same spot.

247
00:18:38,008 --> 00:18:43,841
That's the burden of being a man,
or the patheticness of it, I guess.

248
00:18:44,577 --> 00:18:50,357
I know that, but it's still painful
watching him like that.

249
00:18:51,094 --> 00:18:53,880
And I end up saying
too much sometimes.

250
00:18:55,355 --> 00:18:59,426
It's okay. We're all struggling.

251
00:19:03,646 --> 00:19:05,019
It's too much.

252
00:19:10,206 --> 00:19:11,422
We can't.

253
00:19:12,056 --> 00:19:13,275
We can.

254
00:19:13,543 --> 00:19:14,743
No, we can't.

255
00:19:15,868 --> 00:19:17,072
Yes, we can.

256
00:19:17,283 --> 00:19:18,498
No, we can't.

257
00:19:20,010 --> 00:19:21,210
Yes, we can.

258
00:19:22,130 --> 00:19:23,335
Nope.

259
00:19:23,349 --> 00:19:24,688
Yes.

260
00:19:25,305 --> 00:19:27,470
- No.
- Yes.

261
00:19:29,649 --> 00:19:30,853
Fine, whatever.

262
00:19:32,232 --> 00:19:38,212
That bastard Nishimura's definitely
getting all worked up over her.

263
00:19:41,764 --> 00:19:43,523
Good night, then.

264
00:19:50,875 --> 00:19:52,095
There's no need.

265
00:19:53,819 --> 00:19:56,692
Sorry about all that, really.
Thanks for the meal.

266
00:19:56,732 --> 00:19:59,139
Thanks again. Good night.

267
00:20:15,034 --> 00:20:16,065
I'm home.

268
00:20:16,105 --> 00:20:17,501
Welcome back.

269
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:21,067
God, I'm beat.

270
00:20:21,107 --> 00:20:22,400
Have you been drinking?

271
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:23,975
Yeah, I was, what of it?

272
00:20:24,015 --> 00:20:25,382
Um, hey...

273
00:20:25,922 --> 00:20:28,189
Wait, did you drink a lot?

274
00:20:28,513 --> 00:20:32,221
Yeah, I did. I deserve a night out
once in a while, too.

275
00:20:32,261 --> 00:20:35,881
I'm stuck taking care of Taro
and you every single day.

276
00:20:36,770 --> 00:20:39,262
Anyway, get out of here.

277
00:21:03,054 --> 00:21:04,537
Move. I wanna sit down.

278
00:21:06,191 --> 00:21:08,986
I mostly decided on the series's tone.

279
00:21:09,026 --> 00:21:12,078
I'll write the draft, you do the final.

280
00:21:13,203 --> 00:21:15,790
God, I'm exhausted...

281
00:22:14,845 --> 00:22:15,845
Next Episode Preview

282
00:22:15,875 --> 00:22:17,341
I don't wanna talk to you.

283
00:22:17,381 --> 00:22:19,201
Turn yourself in. You forced it, right?

284
00:22:19,241 --> 00:22:21,035
Hey, quit joking around.

285
00:22:21,075 --> 00:22:22,846
I shouldn't have taken this job.

286
00:22:22,886 --> 00:22:24,695
I am seriously disgusted with you.

287
00:22:24,735 --> 00:22:27,260
Not doing it at all is lonely.

288
00:22:27,300 --> 00:22:29,522
It always comes back to that.
